The character was introduced to audiences in the summer of 1999 as the fianc√©e of the late Prince Richard Winslow. Crystal Chappell originated the role and played it until the end of the series. For her portrayal, the actress was nominated five times for Outstanding Supporting Actress at the Daytime Emmy Awards, winning the award in 2002.
